data.description: Great home in established Mantlebrook Estate within walking distance of Thorntree Country Club. The living room has a cozy fireplace opening to the perfect kitchen with tons of cabinets and a dining area.  This home is in a Cul-de-sac and backs up to a greenbelt is perfect for a growing family. There is space for everyone including pets. 4th bedroom can be used as a Mother-In-Law suite The neighborhood is very quiet and there are nearby parks and a waterpark for parents and the kids to enjoy.
